						<div class="postbody">Another thing I often do, is keep the header as a seperate 16-byte file, then in my .bat file that builds it, it does a "copy /b header+rom rom.nes" type of operation.  But that's largely because having the header built-in is a disadvantage for me.  When I use my ROM emulator for testing, the header is of no use.</div>

